[dramatic organ music]

12
00:01:09.820 --> 00:01:12.156
No country owns football.

13
00:01:13.616 --> 00:01:19.914
This is a common. collective.
human piece of cultural capital.

14
00:01:23.584 --> 00:01:27.713
This is the place that we celebrate
our collective humanity

15
00:01:28.964 --> 00:01:33.427
more intensely
and on a larger scale than anything.

16
00:01:34.136 --> 00:01:39.433
The World Cup is simply the most unifying
universal thing that humanity does.

17
00:01:42.645 --> 00:01:46.023
And it really matters
that the people who run it

18
00:01:46.106 --> 00:01:50.694
actually represent a collective humanity.

19
00:01:53.322 --> 00:01:57.868
And if it is full of self-serving
and corrupt individuals.

20
00:01:57.952 --> 00:02:03.249
and self-serving and malign states.
there is a problem.

21
